sequenceDiagram
    participant Data as Validation Set
    participant Model as Model
    participant Grid as Grid Search
    participant Metrics as Metrics
    participant Boot as Bootstrap
    participant Pareto as Pareto Analysis
    participant Out as Output

    Data->>Model: validation samples

    loop ∀ token t
        Model->>Model: forward pass
        Model->>Grid: H(t), c(t), ŷ(t), y(t)
    end

    Note over Grid: Parameter space<br/>θ_H ∈ [0.1, 1.5]<br/>θ_c ∈ [0.5, 0.99]<br/>30 × 30 = 900 points

    loop ∀ (θ_H, θ_c)
        Grid->>Grid: τ = (H > θ_H) ∧ (c < θ_c)
        Grid->>Metrics: TP, FP, FN, TN

        Note over Metrics: P = TP/(TP+FP)<br/>R = TP/(TP+FN)

        Metrics->>Metrics: F₀.₅ = 1.25·PR/(0.25P+R)
        Metrics->>Boot: F₀.₅ score
    end

    Note over Boot: n = 1000 iterations<br/>95% confidence interval

    Boot->>Pareto: scores + CI

    Note over Pareto: Trade-off analysis<br/>F-score vs. LLM cost

    Pareto->>Out: argmax F₀.₅

    Note over Out: θ*_H = 0.583<br/>θ*_c = 0.787
